# 🔄 FLOW الكامل للنظام

---

## 1️⃣ تسجيل شراء المنتجات (Purchase Batch)

```text
Admin purchases stock
    ↓
Create purchase_batch record
    ↓
Store:
- quantity
- unit_cost
- total_cost
    ↓
Increase inventory stock
2️⃣ تحديث المخزون حسب الدفعات (Batch Tracking)
New batch created
    ↓
Link batch to product inventory
    ↓
System tracks:
- FIFO (first in first out)
- remaining quantity per batch
3️⃣ تسجيل بيع (Sale Creation)
User selects product
    ↓
System detects:
- selling_type (DECANT / FULL / UNIT)
- tier (A/B/C)
- size (if exists)
    ↓
Fetch price from pricing system (Phase 2)
    ↓
Create sale record
4️⃣ خصم المخزون (Product Inventory Deduction)
Sale confirmed
    ↓
Deduct product quantity:
- ml for perfumes
- g for oil-based products
- pcs for items
    ↓
Update inventory balance
5️⃣ استهلاك المواد التشغيلية (Material Consumption)
Sale confirmed
    ↓
System applies recipe rules:

Example:
- 1ml perfume → 0.2ml alcohol
- 1 bottle used per full sale
- packaging used per unit
    ↓
Deduct from material stock:
- alcohol
- bottles
- packaging
6️⃣ تسجيل التكلفة الفعلية للبيع
After sale completion
    ↓
Calculate:
- product cost (from batch FIFO)
- material cost (alcohol + packaging)
    ↓
Store in sale_costs table
7️⃣ تسجيل الفاقد والتلف (Waste System)
Admin reports loss
    ↓
Examples:
- broken bottle
- spilled perfume
- expired stock
    ↓
Deduct from inventory
    ↓
Add cost to loss tracking
8️⃣ حساب الربح الحقيقي (Later Stage)
Profit = Sale Price
         - Product Cost
         - Material Cost
         - Loss Allocation
🧴 أمثلة واقعية
🧴 Lacoste White (Decant System)
Sale:
- 5ml sold → 25 LYD

Cost:

batch cost (old stock)
alcohol usage (1ml)
packaging fraction

Profit calculated after deduction


