## 💎 Dior Sauvage (Full Bottle)

```text
Sale:
- 200ml → 1800 LYD

Cost:
- full batch cost
- bottle + packaging

Profit = net difference
🌿 بخور
Sale:
- 1 piece

Cost:
- material cost per piece
- packaging cost
🪵 وشق (gram system)
Sale:
- 10g

Cost:
- cost per gram batch
